      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、ファッションショーを見ていた方から\n新しく仕事をもらえるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't expect to get a new job offer from someone\nwho saw the fashion show…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.7999999683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "知り合いが紹介してくれたんです。ついでに新曲の\n衣装を着たプロモ用の写真を撮ってもらえるみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My acquaintance introduced me to them. They also said\nthey’d take some promotional photos of us in our new outfits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8666662534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_casino-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "casino-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.3666660786
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり、なんでも頼んでみるものですね\nお願いするだけならタダですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really should ask for things whenever you can.\nAsking doesn’t cost anything‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7999995868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ライブも大成功したし、バッグも無事に戻ってきたし！\nいいことって重なるものですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live show was a huge success‚ and I got my bag back safe and sound!\nGood things really do come in bunches.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9666652362,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.6680653999965,
          "startTime": 32.6333333016
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_casino-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "casino-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.433331728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、知り合いが呼んでる\nそれじゃあ、行ってきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ my acquaintance is calling me.\nI’ll be right back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6333319028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "『こういうポーズで……うん、通訳ありがとう\n表情は、そうね……』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‘In this pose… Yeah‚ thanks for translating.\nThe expression‚ like this…’",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0333322843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "『普段の撮影より、場所も衣装も派手だから\n空気感に合わせるようにするわね』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "‘The location and outfits are flashier than my usual shoots‚\nso I’ll try to match the vibe.’",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9666696866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "カジノを楽しみにやって来る人達を\n引きつける表情と仕草を意識して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to give off an air that will attract\nthe people coming to enjoy the casino…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7333345731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（普段の撮影とは雰囲気から何からまるで違うのに）\n（しっかりと自分を出してる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The atmosphere is completely different from her usual shoots‚）\n（But she’s completely owning it.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5666681607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（どんな場所でも自分の武器をしっかり）\n（見せつける……franさんの本領発揮だな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She can showcase her strengths no matter）\n（where she is… fran-san is in her element.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5333345731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
