    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～、ファッションショーだけじゃなくて\n撮影のギャラまでその場でもらえるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew~‚ not only did I get paid for the fashion show‚\nbut I also got paid for the photo shoot on the spot‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9333391507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "本当にちょうど良かったわね。このギャラを\n元手にすれば、ギャンブルなんかより確実に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "it really worked out perfectly. If I use this money\nas seed money‚ it’s a much surer bet than gambling…",
        "id": ""
      },
