      "text": "……ん？\n知り合いのカミーユさんと連絡してるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hm?\nAre you contacting your acquaintance‚ Camille-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4666704495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
