    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、さっきカジノで知り合った\n海外のセレブと連絡を取ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I’m contacting a foreign celebrity\nwhom I met at the casino earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8000037829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "私のことを凄く気に入ってくれたみたいで……\n「そんなあなたにいい投資の話がある」ですって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They seemed to really like me…\nand said‚ “I have a great investment opportunity for you”!",
        "id": ""
