      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.5333288034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "AI関連の事業投資らしいんですけど\n話を聞けば聞くほど将来性しか見えないなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently‚ it’s an investment in an AI-related business‚\nand the more I hear about it‚ the more promising it seems.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3333313942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.1666601022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
