      "text": "「確実に儲かるから、今の内に出来るだけ沢山の\n金額を投資した方がいい」って言われてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They told me‚ “It’s a surefire way to make money‚\nso it’s best to invest as much as you can right now”.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6333313942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0666601022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "利回りも凄く良くて……\n配当を毎月支払ってくれるんですって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The return on investment is incredible…\nand the dividends will be paid every month!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2333313942,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……やめておいた方がいいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… I think it’s best to avoid that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3999898751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.9999852975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "えっ。ど、どうしてですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? W-why!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.9999852975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんから、芸能界での似たような話は\n山ほど聞いてきましたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve heard countless similar stories from Saegusa-san\nabout the entertainment industry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.9333232562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺自身、星見プロが東京に来てからはそういう話を\nよく持ちかけられてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been approached with similar propositions myself\nsince Hoshimi Productions came to Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.966662693,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.9666560332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……じゃあ、この話って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… so‚ that means this offer is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.9666560332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ametown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ametown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.8666560332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "詐欺の可能性が高いですね。この話に乗ろうものなら\n起業のための努力が全て無駄になってしまいますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s highly likely to be a scam. If you fall for this‚\nall your efforts to start your business will be wasted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.7999939918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
