      "text": "今回は女神どころか悪魔ですよ、多分ですが\nまた、ロケ弁生活になってもいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time‚ it’s probably a devil‚ not a goddess.\nAre you okay with going back to eating only boxed lunches again?",
        "id": ""
